Text: Re ISDA Master between MSCS and Enron Nth America Cc I am the person looking to transact deals with Enron North America I speak to a number of people at Enron but my main contact is Aaron Armstrong I would expect to trade interest rate swaps and options government bonds and repos I hope this helps If there is anything that I can do to speed up the process please let me know Kind regards Chris Mitchell Matthew Flett wrote Dear Sara I now attach a draft schedule to an ISDA Master Agreement between Morgan Stanley Capital Services Inc and Enron North America Corp I would be grateful if you could review the revised draft and revert with any comments that you may have I will also be forwarding you a draft Credit Support Annex for your review in due course I would be grateful if you could acknowledge receipt of this email and confirm that you are the appropriate contact at Enron North America to negotiate this ISDA Do not hesitate to contact me with any queries that you may have Regards Matthew Flett Name Type unspecified type applicationoctetstream Encoding base Download Status Not downloaded with message ChristopherMitchellvcf
